</code></pre>
<pre><code class="lang-auto">private double mAdjustmentAngle = 0;
</code></pre>
<pre><code class="lang-auto">public static final boolean PRACTICE_BOT = false;
</code></pre>
<p>If the getGyroAngle() doesn’t return anything , l think that l can’t even drive field oriented .</p>
