dax1234","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/www.chiefdelphi.com/mendax1234/{size}/156242_2.png","created_at":"2021-09-08T15:19:29.593Z","cooked":"<p>Sorry for responding so late. Now l know that it is really important for me. However , since l am a senior high school student. l am under great pressure of the college entrance examination. l ask this mainly because l am at school during this period of time. And l am very busy due to a lot of schoolwork and homework. However , l don’t give up , though entering FIRST does little good to the College entrance in our country.  But l think this really does much good to what l will do in the future. So, really thanks to give me courage and motion to move forward on the road of FRC! Really thanks!</p>
